# Performance Comparison Between Bare Metal, Virtual Machine and Docker

## Description

This experiment evaluates the impact of different execution environments on system performance.

## Benchmarks

### CPU Benchmark

Measures computational performance using prime number calculations.

Metrics:
- Average latency
- 99th percentile latency
- Total execution time


### Memory Benchmark

Measures random memory access performance.

Metrics:
- Total execution time
- Memory throughput


### I/O Benchmark

Measures sequential file write performance.
